<br />\n睇完覺得內容係有偏頗嘅咪屌<br />\n仲話有獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本就十足十依家啲廢老咁<br />\n唔聽唔睇唔了解<br />\n一睇個表面 係咪都屌咗先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b91bd01173e74e9ff6e575a6e9ad498bf712571","tid":1514864,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"真分裂又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！"},{"pid":"dd1cf8758889f7f61c44fb945a3d819b3ba28965","tid":1514864,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"垃圾片，專注做自己嘢好過係度打飛機 以為自己就嚟贏"},{"pid":"c9fbfc055fffd58194920d630a28689f3a6ae4e5","tid":1514864,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"日日都咁講㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec468ba917d68d5e4f580b442c99ad1b7f964f4","tid":1514864,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"睇完片先開屌得唔得"},{"pid":"3ac1c944127767037865d3c0408acac58575ceb9","tid":1514864,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4f3b8e248f373564c73f03d9e89aacfba6916b","tid":1514864,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MXYfzEoxXgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMXYfzEoxXgQ&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=e9f3d598\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MXYfzEoxXgQ</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關我撚事牙<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce695c02eb6f3cc4e65054c3a4bde73f8c580b60","tid":1514864,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ec468ba917d68d5e4f580b442c99ad1b7f964f4","tid":